  <summary date="2019-08-16T13:18:06Z" status="Introduced in House">Measuring Real Income Growth Act of 2018

This bill requires the Bureau of Economic Analysis to include estimates pertaining to various income groups&#160;in its gross domestic product analyses. Such analyses shall include estimates pertaining to each of the 10 deciles of income as discreet groups and the highest 1% of income as a group.</summary>
